headline: Does Cisco's Recent 28.8% Price Jump Still Offer Investors Value in 2025?
summary: Trying to decide what to do with Cisco Systems stock? If you’re like most investors, you’ve noticed the momentum. Cisco’s shares recently closed at $70.27 and, over the past five years, they’ve more than doubled, up an impressive 128.2%. Even over just the past year, Cisco has delivered a 28.8% gain. More recently, in the last month alone, the stock is up 4.0% following a solid 1.7% jump this past week. That kind of steady growth naturally raises two questions: Is there more upside to come,...
